%% Mermaid diagram describing the current book-review request flow

flowchart TD

    Visitor([User Browser])

    Routes{{`routes/web.php`}}

    BookController[[`App\\Http\\Controllers\\BookController`]]
    ReviewController[[`App\\Http\\Controllers\\ReviewController`]]

    ReviewRequest[[`App\\Http\\Requests\\ReviewRequest`]]

    BookModel[[`App\\Models\\Book`]]
    ReviewModel[[`App\\Models\\Review`]]

    Cache[(Cache)]
    DB[(Database)]

    Visitor -->|HTTP GET| Routes

    Routes -->|`books.index`, `books.show`| BookController
    BookController -->|filter & scope queries| BookModel
    BookController -->|cache remember| Cache
    Cache --> BookController
    BookModel -->|Eloquent ORM| DB
    BookController -->|returns Blade views (`books.index`, `books.show`)| Visitor

    Routes -->|`books.reviews.create`| ReviewController
    ReviewController -->|returns Blade view (`books.reviews.create`)| Visitor

    Routes -->|POST `books/{book}/reviews`| ReviewController
    ReviewController -->|validated data| ReviewRequest
    ReviewRequest --> ReviewController
    ReviewController -->|`reviews()->create()`| ReviewModel
    ReviewModel -->|belongsTo| BookModel
    ReviewModel -->|persist| DB
    ReviewController -->|redirect to `books.show`| Visitor

